<h2>Exhilarating Ski Group Holidays with Inghams!</h2>
<br />
<p>Ski holidays were simply made for groups! Fun and camaraderie on the piste and enjoying an après-ski drink or two, lively chatter over dinner, shared photos and memories to take home – skiing offers all the perfect ingredients for a really great group holiday. <br /><br />At Inghams, we've been taking groups skiing for over 80 years and we love doing it. <br /><br />"Why should I get a group together?" We hear you ask - well, Inghams offer many benefits for groups, with <strong>superb group discounts</strong> (particularly good if you stay at one of our <a data-udi="umb://document/b2d4d8c45f52419a930b506f14a670df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b2d4d8c45f52419a930b506f14a670df}" title="Chalet, 'Xtra Chalet' &amp; Chalet Hotel Holidays">chalets, Chalet Hotels or Xtra Chalets</a>) being just the tip of the iceberg. <br /><br /><strong>Scroll on</strong> to find out what benefits you can receive, how are group discounts work and which properties we recommend for your group size. <br /><br />Or, if you'd like to speak to one of our tried and trusted reservations consultants, please give us a call.</p>
