<h2>Inghams Bonus Benefits for Groups &amp; group leaders</h2>
<br />
<p><strong>Free lift pass:</strong> <br /><br /><span style="background-color: #ff9900;">assasasas</span> for group leaders! Available in most European resorts on groups of 15 guests or more, when all group members pre-book their lift-pass with us.</p>
<p><strong>Free name changes:</strong> up to 4 weeks before your departure date on all our charter flights.</p>
<p><strong>Free lift-pass delivery:</strong> all pre-booked lift passes will be delivered to you on the transfer coach or on arrival in resort.</p>
<p><strong>Group dining:</strong> we can reserve group seating for you on all catered or half board holidays, to allow your group to dine together each evening.</p>
<p><strong>Free thinking time:</strong> We will gladly put the initial group enquiries 'on option' for you, safe-guarding your chosen holiday whilst allowing the group leader time to contact group members, confirm details and arrange deposit payments, before confirming the booking.</p>
<p><strong>Flexible flying:</strong> fly from a choice of 21 UK airports, and we will still apply your group reduction to all group members, as long as all book on the same date for the same accommodation.</p>
<p><strong>Group ski lessons:</strong> Subject of course to ski ability levels, we will always arrange for group members to ski together in the same ski school classes. Dedicated lessons exclusively for your group of 10 or more are also available on request in many resorts.</p>
<p><strong>Free group seating:</strong> when flying on our charter flights.</p>
<p><strong>Pre-bookable ski-packs:</strong> all your group's lift-pass, ski-hire and tuition requirements can be sorted out and paid in advance, ensuring your week gets off to the smoothest possible start!</p>
<p><strong>Free travel insurance for group leaders:</strong> when at least ten adult group members book Inghams insurance.</p>
<h2>'2 For 1 Ski/Board &amp; Boot Hire</h2>
<p><strong>Any members of your group pre-booking their lift pass with Inghams will be entitled to '2-FOR-1' red or blue ski/board hire. If your group comprises of an odd number, one person will receive a 50% reduction.</strong> Available in all properties in France, Austria, Switzerland, Italy, Andorra &amp; Slovenia on all dates.</p>
<h2>Exclusive Private Transfers</h2>
<p><strong>If your group numbers 25 or more we will arrange a FREE exclusive private transfer by coach direct to your resort.</strong></p>
<p>No waiting around at the airport. Just collect your luggage and hit the road! And if you’ve pre-booked your lift passes through Inghams they will normally be delivered to you on the coach to help you get on the slopes as quickly as possible.</p>
<p>Talk to your Personal Groups Advisor when you confirm your booking to make the arrangements.</p>
<p>Your group must number 25 or more and all members of the group must travel on the same flight. For operational reasons, we must reserve the right to withdraw this offer at short notice in the event of flight delays or diversions when it may be necessary to operate coaches to their maximum capacity. This offer must be pre-booked and arranged in advance through your Personal Groups Advisor.</p>
