<h2>Group sizes</h2>
<p>Our generous group reductions start from groups as small as 6 guests and from there upwards, the sky really is the limit! <strong>Up to 1 in 6 go free</strong> on many dates with up to <strong>1¾ </strong><strong>free</strong> places for a group of 10, up to <strong>2¼ free</strong> places for a group of 15, and so on. </p>
<p><br />For example, if your basic price is £599pp and you're a group of 10, travelling on a <strong>Super-Value</strong> date, you simply multiply £599 by 1.75, meaning you'll receive a £1,048.25 discount.<br /><br />Scroll on to find out how these discounts can apply to your group.</p>
