<h2>Inghams recommends: chalets, Chalet Hotels &amp; Xtra Chalets for Groups</h2>
<p>If you're looking to get the best possible value for your group ski holiday, then booking one of our <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-types/chalet-chalet-xtra-chalet-hotel-holidays">chalets, Chalet Hotels or Xtra Chalets</a> really is the only way forward - here's why:</p>
<ul>
<li>you'll receive the <strong>biggest and best group discounts </strong></li>
<li>they range in size meaning you always have options</li>
<li>if they're fully available, you can book them for <strong>exclusive use for your party</strong>, meaning you'll have the place to yourselves</li>
<li>you'll receive fantastic catering (our <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/accommodation-options/chalet-hotel">Chalet Hotel meals</a> were rated "good" or "excellent" by 95% of guests last season), with skier's breakfast, afternoon tea and 4 course evening meals with complimentary wine</li>
<li>Our <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/accommodation-options/chalet">chalet meals</a> were rated ("good" or "excellent" by 96% of guests last season), with skier's breakfast, afternoon tea and 3 course evening meals with complimentary wine</li>
<li><strong>Free</strong> Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Plus much more!<br /><br /></li>
</ul>
<p>Here's just a selection of our favourite chalets, Chalet Hotels and Xtra Chalets depending on your group size:</p>
